addressed are how to avoid any appearance of personal and 
financial conflict of interest how to deal with lapses in 
behavior whether jobrelated or not how should we properly 
regulate interaction between employees and outside groups what 
perks are proper and which are out of bounds 
top leadership must give forth clear and explicit signals 
lest any confusion or uncertainty exist over what is and is not 
permissible conduct thornburgh said 
